(Corrects  Tim Cook ’s name in first paragraph.)  Apple Inc. (AAPL)  Chief Executive Officer
 Steve Jobs  said he’s resigning and recommended Tim Cook be named
his successor.  Jobs said he would like to continue as chairman.  To contact the reporter on this story:
